	dprr:hasNoteText "24 Münzer (RE) would emend this name to Lucanius, a name which appears on. Pompeius Strabo's staff (ILS 8888), and in a Lex Lucania mentioned by Varro (Sat. Men. 67, in Nonius 309L)." .
